Subject: [RFC PATCH 6/8] drm/ttm/pool: Provide a helper to shrink pages.
Date: Fri, 29 Mar 2024 15:57:05 +0100
Message-ID: <20240329145707.3087-7-thomas.hellstrom@linux.intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.44.0
